text: Anita Nemtin (born 5 December 1969) is a Hungarian equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal
